31
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:50,359
- You're dismissed.
- Yes, President Fu.

32
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:05,210
Brother.

33
00:03:05,210 --> 00:03:10,010
Judging by your expression, you seem to already know about this.

34
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,730
What are you insinuating?

35
00:03:12,730 --> 00:03:15,839
