36
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:18,530
If I hand this record to the shareholders,

37
00:03:18,530 --> 00:03:23,050
do you think Zeyi can ever hope to secure his place?

38
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:26,610
Are you threatening me?

39
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:31,860
I know he's your son.

40
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:35,030
You'd forgive any mistakes he makes.

41
00:03:35,030 --> 00:03:39,199
