42
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:43,050
it'll not be a problem between the two of you.

43
00:03:50,220 --> 00:03:54,750
Shengrong, I am well aware of your contributions.

44
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:58,590
I will give you the reward you deserve.

45
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:07,570
