51
00:04:26,039 --> 00:04:31,499
I'll make you pay if you ever try to harm my son! You...

52
00:04:31,499 --> 00:04:34,050
Brother? Brother!

53
00:04:34,050 --> 00:04:36,750
Brother! Brother!

54
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,310
What's wrong?

55
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:40,459
