56
00:04:40,459 --> 00:04:42,470
The medicine...

57
00:04:44,540 --> 00:04:47,399
Hang in there, Brother! Hang in there!

58
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:38,020
Help! Help!

59
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:42,170
