114
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:51,110
Uncle Fu, thank you for your care over the years.

115
00:11:51,110 --> 00:11:54,010
This is a token of appreciation.

116
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:04,930
After today, I'll go abroad to further my studies.

117
00:12:04,930 --> 00:12:07,559
I hope to have your blessing.

118
00:12:07,559 --> 00:12:12,899
That's great. But remember to come back after you finish your studies.

119
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:27,279
It looks great. Thanks.

120
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:31,130
