I want to take a walk by myself.

140
00:15:50,450 --> 00:15:52,790
You should go home.

141
00:15:52,790 --> 00:15:55,139
All right. Stay safe.

142
00:15:55,139 --> 00:15:57,439
- See you.
- Sure.

143
00:15:59,920 --> 00:16:01,570
Zhixia.

144
